    <item><title>ChristianMahnke.de: Christmas 2024</title>
        <link>https://christianmahnke.de/post/christmas-2024-2</link>
        <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 10:00:00 +0200</pubDate>
        <guid>https://projektemacher.org/en/post/christianmahnke/post/christmas-2024-2/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;Merry Christmas to all readers, this year the traditional present comes a little earlier&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; as I am offering a &lt;a href=&#34;https://projektemacher.org/post/christmas-2024-workshop/&#34;&gt;workshop&lt;/a&gt; on the subject.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Almost a tradition: The &lt;a href=&#34;./instructions-2023-1.pdf&#34;&gt;craft instructions I&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;./instructions-2023-2.pdf&#34;&gt;craft instructions II&lt;/a&gt; for the Christmas cards.&lt;/p&gt;




&lt;figure class=&#34;christmas-card&#34;&gt;
    
        &lt;img src=&#34;https://projektemacher.org/en/post/christianmahnke/post/christmas-2024-2/card-2024-1.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Christmas card I&#34;/&gt; &lt;figcaption&gt;
                
                &lt;p&gt;
                    Completed card 1
                    
                        
                        &lt;/p&gt;
                
            &lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;





&lt;figure class=&#34;christmas-card&#34;&gt;
    
        &lt;img src=&#34;https://projektemacher.org/en/post/christianmahnke/post/christmas-2024-2/card-2024-2.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Christmas card II&#34;/&gt; &lt;figcaption&gt;
                
                &lt;p&gt;
                    Completed card 2
                    
                        
                        &lt;/p&gt;
                
            &lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The wallpaper used is from &lt;a href=&#34;http://zeitzeug.de/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Zeitzeug&lt;/a&gt; in Göttingen and also shown in high resolution at &lt;a href=&#34;https://vorsatzpapier.projektemacher.org/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Vorsatzpapier&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://vorsatzpapier.projektemacher.org/post/tapete-26/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Card 1 - Wallpaper 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://vorsatzpapier.projektemacher.org/post/tapete-38/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Card 1 - Wallpaper 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://vorsatzpapier.projektemacher.org/post/tapete-36/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Card 2 - Wallpaper 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://vorsatzpapier.projektemacher.org/post/tapete-37/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Card 2 - Wallpaper 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Translated with &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.DeepL.com/Translator&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;www.DeepL.com/Translator&lt;/a&gt; (free version)&lt;/p&gt;
